OL,4,CLeon: Billionaire Issa brothers buy
OL,5,Cfast food chain
OL,6, The billionaire Issa brothers who own
OL,7, Asda have bought the British fast food
OL,8, chain, Leon.
OL,10,FMore than 70 Leon restaurants across
OL,11,Fthe UK and Europe have been sold to the
OL,12,Fbrothers' giant petrol forecourt
OL,13,Fbusiness EG Group.
OL,15,FIn a joint statement, Mohsin Issa and
OL,16,FZuber Issa said the firm was a
OL,17,F"fantastic brand we have long admired".
OL,19,FLeon boss John Vincent, who co-founded
OL,20,Fthe firm in 2004, said: "In some ways
OL,21,Fthis is a sad day for me."
